text: Duchess Elisabeth of Württemberg (; born 2 February 1933) is a member of the House of Württemberg and a Duchess of Württemberg. She was married to Prince Antoine of Bourbon-Two Sicilies, a member of the House of Bourbon-Two Sicilies and a Princess of Bourbon-Two Sicilies. ==Titles and styles== *2 February 1933 – 22 January 2022: Her Royal Highness Duchess Elisabeth of Württemberg, Princess of Württemberg ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:French princesses Category:German princes and princesses Category:People from Stuttgart
title: Duchess Elisabeth of Württemberg (b. 1933)
